HEADWORD: Rickety
<hw>Rick"et*y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Affected
with rickets.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Feeble in the joints; imperfect; weak;
shaky.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

